Marlyne Barrett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marlyne_Barrett 0 Marlyne Nayokah Barrett (born Afflack, on September 13, 1978) is an American actress, known for her roles on television. She had a recurring role from 2006 to 2008 as Nerese Campbell in the HBO crime drama The Wire and in 2007, she had a recurring role as Felicia Marquand in the FX legal drama Damages. In 2015, she began starring as Head Charge Nurse Maggie Lockwood in the NBC medical drama Chicago Med.
